# google.list — Google AI surface (Gemini / AI Studio / DeepMind / NotebookLM)
# Target group: Google  (Select-only, prefer Japan, backup Singapore; avoid HK)
# Format: one rule per line, TYPE,value  (NO trailing policy).
# NOTE: broad Google coverage comes from the remote blackmatrix7 Google
# rule-set (retargeted to the Google group). These specific AI subdomains are
# listed locally so Gemini/AI-Studio deterministically hit the Google group.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gemini.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,aistudio.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ai.google.dev
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,generativelanguage.googleapis.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,notebooklm.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bard.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.google
DOMAIN,labs.google
